high_descs: Take a few steps forward and then turn left to the white table.
Pick up the knife close to the spoon on the table.
Turn right, head to the fridge, and turn right towards the sink.
Place the knife in the square pan in the sink.
Take the pan out of the sink.
Turn around, take a few steps forward, and then turn left towards the white table on your right.
Place the pan to the left of the brown pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a square pan with a knife on the white table.

high_descs: Go to the white table on your right.
Pick up the knife under the left head of lettuce.
Turn around and go to the sink, to the left of the dishwasher.
Place the knife in the black pan inside the sink.
Pick up the black pan with the knife inside it, from the sink.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen until you reach the white table to your right.
Place the black pan with the knife inside it, on  the far left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan, containing a knife on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table on your left.
Grab the knife off the table.
Walk to the kitchen sink.
Place the knife inside the pan.
Grab the pan with the knife in it.
Walk back to the kitchen table you got the knife off of.
Place the pan to the left of the frying pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife inside a pan to set up on a table.
